name: Niyati NC History
description:
Niyati Clothing NC History Tee
Brand new is the Niyati Clothing NC History Tee. This tee is very unique because if you look closely you will see the history of North Carolina inside it, is made of 100% cotton and has very high quality printing! The shirt has a washing that makes it feel even more pleasant and soft when you wear it.
The Niyati Clothing Banner Tee's are available in:
- Black
- White
- Charcoal Grey
Available in S - XXL
